Selity
============================================

http://selity.org

Selity software appliance provides complete hosting automation for Linux platforms.
Selity offers an easy-to-use graphical interface for administrators, resellers and
custommers, and complete functionality to manage the server and its components.

Selity was designed for professional Hosting Service Providers (HSPs).

With Selity you are able configure your server and applications, create customers with
domains with a few point-and-click operations that take less than a minute. There is
no limit to the number of administrators, resellers, customers and domains that can
be created.

Enjoy the power of Selity
Your Selity Team


INSTALLATION
============

Select the folder of the distribution you are using inside the docs directory. For
Debian: ./docs/Debian/INSTALL If there is none, select Debian and try it with this
one.

You have successfully installed Selity on a non-listed distribution? Great, send us
your install instructions.

